{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/09/hellblade-senuas-sacrifice/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7494e53a-4964-5561-834b-8a4bad5d984a","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<h2 id=\"初次印象\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E6%AC%A1%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1\" aria-label=\"初次印象 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>初次印象</h2>\n<p>初次在 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/JbQSpfWUs4I?t=273\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Unreal Engine 的运动捕捉实时渲染演示</a>上见过，但没注意到是这个游戏。\n因为之前对<a href=\"/2015/04/memo-of-qq-april-fool-fun/\">渲染和运动捕捉研究</a>过一点，所以对整个系统的实时性和画面效果留下很深印象。</p>\n<p>后来<a href=\"/2019/08/talk-about-xbox-1x-after-1-year\">买 Xbox</a> 了试用 Game Pass 时候又看到，于是开始深入体验这款游戏。\n游戏环境氛围音效动画非常棒，带耳机听<a href=\"https://www.hellblade.com/development-diary-24-hearing-voices/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">萦绕在主角脑海的耳语</a>都会有高潮。\n喜欢凯尔特、北欧神话背景世界观的独特风格。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/aeb1f/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.315789473684205%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/5ed05/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 190w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/9d76b/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 380w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/33466/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 760w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/ca244/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 1140w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/674e9/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 1350w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/89129/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 190w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/0036d/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 380w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/e484a/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 760w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/32d87/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 1140w,\n/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/aeb1f/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 1350w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/e484a/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg\"\n            alt=\"hellblade-astonishing-scene\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>画面氛围与主角 Senua 分裂人格而萦绕的多个耳语声音，让我深深体会到她的迷惑、绝望和痛苦，而跟随剧情的推进却又无不透露出她的坚强、执着和勇敢。\n进入上图那个场景时被震撼到了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"背景历史与文化\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" aria-label=\"背景历史与文化 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>背景历史与文化</h2>\n<p>游戏故事背景来自于凯尔特、北欧历史与神话，这个看<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KQUwYYS4QyE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">“就知道玩游戏”的解读视频</a>说的很好，\n特别是对游戏结局 Senua 与 海拉，到底是谁杀死谁的解读独到且深刻，我很赞同这个解读。对剧情的截然不同解读，和游戏标题 Hellblade 细想耐人寻味。</p>\n<p>像我这种没法通关的人，只好看这个解读来“云通关”了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"bug-卡住剧情\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bug-%E5%8D%A1%E4%BD%8F%E5%89%A7%E6%83%85\" aria-label=\"bug 卡住剧情 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bug 卡住剧情</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/aeb1f/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.315789473684205%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/5ed05/hellblade-torch-bug.webp 190w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/9d76b/hellblade-torch-bug.webp 380w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/33466/hellblade-torch-bug.webp 760w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/ca244/hellblade-torch-bug.webp 1140w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/674e9/hellblade-torch-bug.webp 1350w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/89129/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg 190w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/0036d/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg 380w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/e484a/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg 760w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/32d87/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg 1140w,\n/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/aeb1f/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg 1350w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a9fae32e57f2434f0f670ee303eaf858/e484a/hellblade-torch-bug.jpg\"\n            alt=\"hellblade-torch-bug\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在黑暗恶魔的侵袭下，我一路乱冲，从一处木板桥上掉下去，掉落的过程中（我猜掉落有2秒钟）我想估计是死了，结果掉到这里。\n没有火把，无法解开这个门的谜题，无限循环卡死在这里了。</p>\n<p>看别人视频，这里应该是在洞口点燃火把，然后靠火光的庇护再往前的。我是被黑暗恶魔侵袭下，只想着快点冲没注意到这个点火处，结果慌乱之中就冲掉下去了。</p>\n<p>这有一段 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PZsMbxvDjLQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">torch bug 卡住剧情</a>的演示视频。</p>\n<p>忍者理论不应该遗留这种问题啊，倒霉还让我给碰上了!</p>","excerpt":"","fields":{"slug":"/2019/09/hellblade-senuas-sacrifice","categorySlugs":["/category/小玩意/","/category/观点/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/游戏/","/tag/xbox/","/tag/地狱之刃/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"游玩《地狱之刃：塞纳的献祭》感受","date":"2019-09-07T10:54:37.121Z","categories":["小玩意","观点"],"description":"在 Unreal Engine 的运动捕捉实时渲染演示上首次见过，留下很深印象。体验该游戏中了解凯尔特、北欧历史神话背景觉得很有意思，但被一个罕见bug卡住剧情无法继续","tags":["游戏","Xbox","地狱之刃"],"slug":"/2019/09/hellblade-senuas-sacrifice","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/e737e/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg","srcSet":"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/e737e/hellblade-astonishing-scene.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/054055ac3c1aa76b6eaca0941589ea0b/e7773/hellblade-astonishing-scene.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/09/update-android-10-and-flash-modem-for-china-telecom-4g"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Pixel 升级 Android 10 并破解电信 4G"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/09/rise-of-the-tomb-raider"},"frontmatter":{"title":"游戏《古墓丽影-崛起》通关感受"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019/09/hellblade-senuas-sacrifice","prevPostSlug":"/2019/09/update-android-10-and-flash-modem-for-china-telecom-4g","nextPostSlug":"/2019/09/rise-of-the-tomb-raider"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}